# Solution: csharp_data_warehouse_expert_012_architectural_understanding_expert_01

## Key Files Identified

### Stream Processing Pipeline Modules
- `/app/project/src/module_72.txt` - **KinesisStreamProcessor**: Primary stream processing entry-point Lambda that ingests Kinesis records, validates envelopes, and applies transformation strategies in real-time
- `/app/project/src/module_80.txt` - **StreamTransformationCoordinator**: High-throughput Kinesis stream processor with reflection-driven strategy discovery and bounded parallelism
- `/app/project/src/module_68.txt` - **TransformationLambda**: Lambda entry-point for Kinesis stream transformation with EventBridge dispatcher for downstream fan-out
- `/app/project/src/module_22.txt` - **CalendarMetricLambda**: Kinesis-triggered Lambda for calendar/meeting telemetry processing

### Batch Processing Pipeline Modules
- `/app/project/src/module_64.txt` - **KpiComputationOrchestrator**: Core batch processing orchestrator reusable across stream and batch (Glue/Step-Functions) pipelines
- `/app/project/src/module_86.txt` - **TransformationOrchestrator**: Infrastructure-agnostic transformation orchestrator designed for batch (Glue/Step-Functions) workloads
- `/app/project/src/module_34.txt` - **KpiComputationEngine**: Strategy registry and KPI computation engine used by batch jobs
- `/app/project/src/module_35.txt` - **TransformationDispatcher**: Batch-capable transformation dispatcher serving both Kinesis streams and Glue batch jobs
- `/app/project/src/module_10.txt` - **KpiTransformationEngine**: Coordinates batch transformation with S3 persistence

### Shared/Core Modules
- `/app/project/src/module_65.txt` - **EventTransformationPipeline**: Dataflow-based pipeline with high startup initialization cost
- `/app/project/src/module_39.txt` - **TransformationEngine**: Transformation engine with registry and retry semantics
- `/app/project/src/module_60.txt` - **KpiStrategyRegistry**: Strategy discovery with attribute-based auto-registration
- `/app/project/src/module_43.txt` - **FocusTimeRatioTransformation**: Async transformation strategy with Timer-based flushing
- `/app/project/src/config.txt` - Configuration layer with `BatchWindowSeconds` setting (default 900 seconds = 15 minutes minimum)
- `/app/project/src/constants.txt` - System constants including Glue job names and resource identifiers

