    33→    /// <summary>
    34→    /// Thin wrapper around any raw event that enters the warehouse.
    35→    /// Envelopes allow us to standardise metadata required for transformation,
    36→    /// without rewriting every single ingestion lambda when an attribute is added later on.
    37→    /// </summary>
    38→    /// <remarks>
    39→    /// The schema mirrors the one emitted by the <c>EventIngressProcessor</c> lambda.
