     7→//  This Lambda listens to a Kinesis stream containing heterogeneous calendar /
     8→//  meeting telemetry.  Each record has a "metricType" attribute that tells the
     9→//  engine what KPI should be derived from the raw payload.  A pluggable
    10→//  strategy registry allows new KPIs to be introduced without redeployment;
    11→//  they simply get loaded from DI (reflection or external assembly).
