#### Justification: How This Overcomes Bottlenecks

| Bottleneck | Solution | Benefit |
|------------|----------|---------|
| **High Startup Cost** (assembly scanning) | Singleton `Lazy<TransformationStrategyRegistry>` that persists across Lambda invocations | Amortizes ~1500ms cold-start across thousands of invocations |
| **TPL Dataflow Overhead** | Direct `Parallel.ForEachAsync` without Dataflow infrastructure | Eliminates 100-300ms pipeline setup per invocation |
